Even the front door staff is terrific; always willing to gladly open any doors for you and to get or arrange for transportation.	For valet parking I like that they have their own garage below the hotel rather than off site.	Location is great - within walking distance of many things and easy reach of the main public transport.	As we were new to the city, she was able to suggest several places to visit and also which public transport to take.	The staff is oustanding and the valet/email/checkin process is excellent.	The hotel is within walking distance to mostly everything, or within inexpensive cab ride distance.